title: The Price Is Zeit 12/3: Warner Bros, Ivanka Trump, 15% ICU, Supreme

description:
On this edition of The Price Is Zeit Jack and Miles discuss Warner Brothers dropping their entire 2021 slate in both theaters and on HBOMax, Ivanka Trump is trying to excuse the nepotism and corruption that got her a job, new Lockdown orders are confusing and ineffective as deaths, cases, and ICU occupancies soar, and an enormous load of Supreme Box Logo tees have gone up for auction at Christie's.
